{"tid":1008629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【TVB】香港股市也實名制?!　中國實名制　香港不實名制　很怪","createTime":"2019-02-04T15:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T16:15:58.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"098da5d31347d549de5475ec671bfaba20517555","tid":1008629,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:42:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/finance/5c580961e60383a0228bb737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Ffinance%2F5c580961e60383a0228bb737&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJzY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=be7c6c0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/finance/5c580961e60383a0228bb737</a><br />\n<br />\n證監會計劃上半年，就港股全面實施「實名制」展開諮詢。香港投資基金公會指，不擔心實名制會影響本港競爭力。<br />\n<br />\n投資基金公會行政總裁黃王慈明表示：「香港的實名(制)，監管機構給予靈活性，實名時可用基金的名，或用基金公司的名。如果(內地)一邊的市場，可以穿透到底看到投資者，但另一邊(香港)又看不到，其實會很怪，即是變了有監管套利，所以在監管機構推這個制度時，其實我們覺得很合理，也是完全支持。」"},{"pid":"88679f7125a5414cc50477a2ca92b5071af7448a","tid":1008629,"uid":39059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"實名左仲點洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4993a7354410bc916f956e57d405b78f7a67a16e","tid":1008629,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88679f7125a5414cc50477a2ca92b5071af7448a","tid":1008629,"uid":39059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"實名左仲點洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"香港已經多咗好多限制<br />\n12萬現金出入已經要開名<br />\n股都開名<img src=\"/assets/faces